==English==

===Etymology===
:From {{AGr.}} '''{{polytonic|[[σύμπτωμα]]}}''' (sumptōma) "a happening, accident, disease" < stem of '''{{polytonic|[[συμπίπτω]]}}''' (sumpiptō) "Ι befall" < '''{{polytonic|[[συν-]]}}''' (sun-) "together" and '''{{polytonic|[[πίπτω]]}}''' (piptō) "I fall"

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Anything that [[indicate]]s, or is [[characteristic]] of,  the [[presence]] of something else; especially a [[perceived]] [[change]] in some [[function]], [[sensation]] or [[appearance]] of a [[patient]] that is [[indicative]] of a [[disease]] or [[disorder]].

====Synonyms====
